desc.zh-Hans:
坦市是在网页游戏bloxd.io的一个城市服，服名tankocity，服主是TANKOMINATOR2。
坦市地铁连接了坦市各个地区的交通，地铁由lao_qiu修建，目前已开通线路有2条（截至2025.6.6）

Tan City is a city server in web game bloxd.io,server name is tankocity,owner name is TANKOMINATOR2.
Tan city railway is built by lao_qiu, and there are currently 2 lines in operation (as of June 6, 2025).
